bnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWxwSRPO.jpg&h=790f6e70&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SFppHWy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSFppHWy.jpg&h=e19526bf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/crrrWh3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcrrrWh3.jpg&h=a6a4c9af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AT2uBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AT2uBA.jpg&h=49346db4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9XXuT3h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9XXuT3h.jpg&h=12f85858&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大埔名物(土產)：香蕉糖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CTbod5f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCTbod5f.jpg&h=0c3e23d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z5SOqbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ5SOqbW.jpg&h=807c236c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n-----------分隔線-----------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">文宣：宣傳片</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oex2SY8Tngw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOex2SY8Tngw&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b5762b24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Oex2SY8Tngw</a><br />\nCredit：一個熱愛大埔，就讀於一間愛學生、<br />\n關心一下代的學校（大埔面積最大嗰間中學）嘅學生自發製作短片<br />\n<br />\n-----------分隔線-----------<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">文宣：Telegram頻道</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TP810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTP810&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rPrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=b3537e7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TP810</a> - 810大埔遊行資訊發佈<br />\n</div>"},{"pid":"92d2f5291ade1c94568ff8254576a95